<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="comment-851">
	<div>

		<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/676ff6cf530af46c0a404abd399a464c?s=50&amp;d=&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' />

		<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/wheatdogg/gravity-deniers-and-the-gravity-of-ignorance/?replytocom=851#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-851", "851", "respond", "186")'>Reply</a>

		<span class="comment-author">
			<a href='http://wgods.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Wilhelm Godschalk</a>
		</span>
		
		<span class="comment-date-link">
			<a href="http://www.computernewbie.info/wheatdogg/gravity-deniers-and-the-gravity-of-ignorance/#comment-851">
				Aug 17,2006 
